The transient photocurrent response of Ag2BiI5 (HIA) provided a valuable means of testing our mechanistic hypothesis derived from Iph-Popt\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
